  "id": "RAW_fa62c6",
  "title": "AI 也需要\"记笔记\"：Karpathy 从 Claude 1.6 万字提示词中看到的未来",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU0MDk3NTUxMA==&mid=2247488909&idx=1&sn=d1a4c0406d32926145fc0a459527d8dd&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-12 08:29:00",
  "author": "歸藏的 AI 工具箱",
  "siteName": "歸藏的AI工具箱",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"揭秘Claude：16739字“秘籍”曝光，聊天机器人不只是模型！\" author=\"歸藏的AI工具箱\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=%E6%8F%AD%E7%A7%98Claude%EF%BC%9A16739%E5%AD%97%E2%80%9C%E7%A7%98%E7%B1%8D%E2%80%9D%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%81&amp;play_length=\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"3072\" source_size=\"3072\" high_size=\"3072\" play_length=\"195000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzU0MDk3NTUxMF8yMjQ3NDg4OTA4\" cover=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ofWbZTuv4DXmCK6OJwibC98PfpCNK0IK20TNKsvXQkfgTDblpVHtxxDibkRoT4ZeIwfhNlo2FN6IHOEedJzuzdoyHibKpSdOnqa/0\" class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n   <span style=\"font-style: italic;color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">如果懒得看内容可以听一下，播客使用 listenhub 制作</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">前几天 Cluade 新的系统提示词泄露了，居然有 16,739 个单词，非常长。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100005254\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e707b097-7092-47c2-b505-3df3409dec00/public\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e707b097-7092-47c2-b505-3df3409dec00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">相比之下，OpenAI 在 ChatGPT 中的 o4-mini 的系统提示有 2,218 个单词，只是 Claude 的 13%。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:medium;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(254, 212, 164);padding:16px 16px 10px;letter-spacing:normal;display:flex;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🎁</span></span></span>\n   <section style=\"\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么是系统提示词</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;min-height:20px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">LLM 的系统提示就是在对话一开始递给 AI 的“一页说明书”，用来告诉它该扮演什么角色、遵守哪些规则、用什么方式回答用户。</span></span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">大概来看一下这么长的提示词里面主要都是一些什么内容：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(20, 86, 240);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 30px;padding-left: 20px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">占比最多的就是工具定义，这里面详细介绍了 Claude 可以调用的 14 个 MCP 的具体信息，短的只有十几行，长的比如谷歌 Drive 搜索的介绍超过了 1700 个字。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">然后是用户偏好和风格这部分主要详细规定了 Claude 应如何表现、回应用户请求，以及哪些该做、哪些不该做。比如处理设计计算的时候需要思考，还有涉及到知识截止日期的问题，用户要求写诗歌的时候应该怎么写等。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\">最后的 引用说明、Artifact说明、搜索说明以及谷歌集成注意事项其实也是关于工具使用的，只不过这部分跟 MCP 无关被单独拿出来了。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100005253\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/46c9fc0c-a0b4-4275-493b-ab5a7c2da600/public\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/46c9fc0c-a0b4-4275-493b-ab5a7c2da600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">而且整个提示词中充满了临时修改的的痕迹，这些修改往往没有使用 XML 或者 Markdown 格式的列表，就是一段话，看起来像是针对一些热点事件或者问题修复打的补丁。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;margin-top:12px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;font-weight:400;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;border-top-right-radius:5px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-top-left-radius:5px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;height:30px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"height: 30px;line-height: 30px;margin-left: 10px;display: flex;\"><span style=\"width: 10px;height: 10px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(255, 95, 86);margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"width: 10px;height: 10px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(255, 189, 46);margin-right: 8px;margin-top: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"width: 10px;height: 10px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(39, 201, 63);margin-top: 10px;\"></span></span></span>\n   <pre style=\"margin: 0px;\"><code style=\"padding:4px 15px 15px;border-bottom-left-radius:5px;display:block;overflow-x:auto;font-size:14px;border-bottom-right-radius:5px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.5;\"><span leaf=\"\">If you&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">are</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">using</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">any</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;gmail tools&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">and</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;the&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">user</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;has instructed you&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">to</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;find messages&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">for</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;a particular person, do&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">NOT</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;assume that person</span><span><span leaf=\"\">'s email. Since some employees and colleagues share first names, DO NOT assume the person who the user is referring to shares the same email as someone who shares that colleague'</span></span><span leaf=\"\">s&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">first</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;name that you may have seen incidentally (e.g. through a previous email&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">or</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;calendar&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">search</span></span><span leaf=\"\">). Instead, you can&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">search</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;the&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">user</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'s email with the first name and then ask the user to confirm if any of the returned emails are the correct emails for their colleagues.</span></span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Claude 整个系统提示词这么长维护和更新甚至版本控制应该都需要一个专门的流程，不然很容易直接上线之后出问题，不知道具体是怎么样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">分享这个除了学习 Cluade 写提示词之外主要是看到今天 Karpathy 发的一个观点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">他受到 Claude 这个提示词的启发说：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前大语言模型（LLM）的学习方式还缺少一种重要的范式，他称之为“系统提示（system prompt）学习</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100005252\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c881b58b-2f72-4280-ef02-617bf8e59100/public\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c881b58b-2f72-4280-ef02-617bf8e59100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">目前我们 LLM 主流的两个主流的学习方式预训练（pretraining）和微调（finetuning，包括监督学习SL和强化学习RL）——都依赖于模型参数的更新，但这与人类的某些学习方式并不完全一致。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:medium;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(254, 212, 164);padding:16px 16px 10px;letter-spacing:normal;display:flex;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🎁</span></span></span>\n   <section style=\"\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">现有 LLM 学习范式</span></span><span></span></p>\n    <ul style=\"color: rgb(20, 86, 240);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 30px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 24px;text-align: left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">预训练（Pretraining）</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：主要用于让模型获得广泛的知识。通过大规模语料库训练，模型学会了语言、常识和世界知识。</span></span></li>\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">微调（Finetuning，SL/RL）</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：让模型形成“习惯性行为”，比如更好地遵循指令、优化对话风格等。这一过程同样是通过调整模型参数实现的。</span></span></li>\n    </ul>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">但是人类在学习新知识或解决新问题时，往往不是直接“改写大脑参数”，而是通过“记笔记”或“自我提醒”的方式，将经验和策略以显式的形式保留下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">例如，当你遇到某类问题时，会总结出“下次遇到类似情况可以这样做”的经验。这种方式更像是在不断编辑自己的“系统提示”，而不是每次都重新训练大脑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">所以“系统提示学习”是一种介于模型参数和外部记忆之间的机制。他认为，LLM 也应该有类似“记笔记”的能力，把解决问题的策略、经验和通用知识以显式文本的方式存储下来，而不是全部依赖参数更新。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">例如上面 Claude 的系统提示，全部都是由人类编写，效率低且难以扩展。Karpathy 认为，理想情况下，模型应该能通过“系统提示学习”自动生成和优化这些提示，就像人类自己总结经验一样。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:medium;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(254, 212, 164);padding:16px 16px 10px;letter-spacing:normal;display:flex;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🎁</span></span></span>\n   <section style=\"\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">系统提示学习的优势</span></span><span></span></p>\n    <ul style=\"color: rgb(20, 86, 240);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top: 0px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 30px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 24px;text-align: left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">更高效的数据利用</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：通过显式的“复盘”或“总结”，模型可以更高效地吸收反馈，比单纯的奖励信号（reward scaler）更高维、更丰富。</span></span></li>\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">更强的泛化能力</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：显式的策略和经验总结有助于模型在新任务中迁移和应用知识。</span></span></li>\n    </ul>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Karpathy 比喻说，当前的 LLM 就像电影《记忆碎片》（Memento）里的主角，没有自己的“备忘录”或“草稿本”，只能靠参数记忆一切，其实藏师傅的网页提示词就已经在充当这种作用了，而且相当一部分是跟 AI 共创的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">他也说</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">“系统提示学习”如果能实现，将成为 LLM 领域一个全新的、强大的学习范式</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">但是也会存在很多的问题需要解决，比如：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(20, 86, 240);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 30px;padding-left: 20px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">如何自动编辑和优化系统提示？</span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">是否需要为“编辑系统”本身设计学习机制？</span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">如何让显式知识逐步转化为模型的“习惯性”参数？</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">系统提示词就像私人助理的指令手册。越详细，结果越精准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">与AI交流时，明确指令胜过模糊表达。学会像Claude的提示词那样，具体说明需求和边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">善用列表、格式和示例。AI更容易理解结构化的指令。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">\"提示工程\"不是高深技术，而是日常沟通技巧的延伸。普通人也能掌握。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">感兴趣的话可以详细的看一下 Claude 的提示词内容，学习一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">而且 Karpathy 这个系统提示学习其实现在也可以半自动的实现一部分，从业者可以参考一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;border-width:1px 0px 